This paper discusses the security implications of data protection regulations, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and privacy (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the technical infrastructure and organizational processes involved in fulfilling data subject rights, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE), databases (cs.DB), and machine learning (cs.LG) as these fields deal with the design and implementation of such systems.
